{{Missing info|make a section for ''Bedrock Edition'' texture atlases ([[atlas.terrain]], atlas.items, atlas.banner, atlas.shield, and atlas.uithumbnail.)}}
Many of the game's textures are compiled into one of several atlases upon resource loading. These are considered by the game to be [[dynamic textures]].

== Summary ==
As of Java Edition 1.21.11, there are 15 atlases which the game generates when loading resources.

All atlases can be saved as an image file via {{key|F3 + S}} to a directory titled "debug" in [[.minecraft]]'s screenshots directory.
